  3,106,"∆êda no a (ebinom) anim bŒµyŒµ fitaa na (ebinom) nso anim bŒµyŒµ tumm no; (yŒµbŒµka akyerŒµ) wÕªn a wÕªn anim tumm no sŒµ: ‚ÄúMogyidie akyi no mopoo nokorŒµ no. Enti monka asotwee no nhwŒµ, Œµnam nokorŒµ a mopoeŒµ no ho nti.‚Äù"
