  4,23,"Y‚Äôabra mo (sŒµ mobŒµware) mo maamenom, ne mo mma mmaa, ne monua mmaa, ne mosewaanom, ne mo maame nua mmaa, ne monua mmarima mma mmaa, ne mo nua mmaa mma mmaa, ne mo maamenom a wÕªn ama mo nufoÕª anom, ne monua mmaa a (monfri eni anaasŒµ sekorÕª na mmom) mone wÕªn anom nufu korÕª, ne moyere nom maamenom, ne momma nnoma mmaa a mona mohwŒµ wÕªn soÕª a wÕª‚ÄôyŒµ moyere nom a moakÕª wÕªn ho mma mmaa; nasŒµ monkÕªÕª wÕªn (maame) ho deŒµ a, ŒµneŒµ bÕªne biara nni moso; Œµna mo mma mmarima a wÕª‚Äôfiri moara mosisi mu yere nom. (Y‚Äôabra mo nso) sŒµ mobŒµka nnua mmaa mmienu abom (aware wÕªn), gyesŒµ deŒµ atwa mu. NokorŒµ sŒµ, NyankopÕªn ne BÕªnefakyŒµ Hene, na ∆Üne MmÕªborÕªhunu Hene"